Metal ore is the raw form of metal, and has a wide variety of practical applications in electronics and general construction.\n\nMetal ore is typically processed into <link=\"REFINEDMETAL\">Refined Metal</link> using the <link=\"ROCKCRUSHER\">Rock Crusher</link> or the <link=\"METALREFINERY\">Metal Refinery</link>.\n\nSome rare metal ores can also be refined in the <link=\"SUPERMATERIALREFINERY\">Molecular Forge</link>.